<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19733624">人经常会突然觉得眼前的事似曾相识,  对于这个现象, 有哪些合理的解释？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="73547" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"> 我想没有一种解释能够完全切中"真理"的, 因为很难检验. 至少, 有哪些看起来靠谱的解释呢?<br><br>相关问题：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/19587685" class="internal"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">zhihu.com/question/1958</span><span class="invisible">7685</span><span class="ellipsis"></span></a>， <a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/19594277" class="internal"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">zhihu.com/question/1959</span><span class="invisible">4277</span><span class="ellipsis"></span></a> </div>


</div>
